trans-unit.source: When implemented in a type, returns a list of zero or more session keys that indicate to a session-state provider which session-state items have to be retrieved.
trans-unit.target: 在型別中實作時，會傳回零或多個工作階段金鑰的清單，向工作階段狀態提供者表示必須擷取的工作階段狀態項目。

trans-unit.source: When a type that implements this interface returns a non-null generic list of strings in the <xref:System.Web.SessionState.IPartialSessionState.PartialSessionStateKeys%2A> property, the list indicates to a session-state provider that the provider should retrieve only the session-state values that are specified in the list.
trans-unit.target: 實作此介面的型別時傳回非 null 泛型清單中的字串<xref:System.Web.SessionState.IPartialSessionState.PartialSessionStateKeys%2A>屬性，清單會指出工作階段狀態提供者提供者應該擷取只在清單中指定的工作階段狀態值。

trans-unit.source: If the type returns a `null` value for the <xref:System.Web.SessionState.IPartialSessionState.PartialSessionStateKeys%2A> property, a session-state provider should get all session-state values.
trans-unit.target: 如果傳回型別`null`值<xref:System.Web.SessionState.IPartialSessionState.PartialSessionStateKeys%2A>屬性，工作階段狀態提供者應取得工作階段狀態的所有值。

trans-unit.source: Gets a list of keys that are associated with session-state values.
trans-unit.target: 取得與工作階段狀態值相關聯的金鑰清單。

trans-unit.source: A generic list of strings that serve as keys for session-state values.
trans-unit.target: 字串的泛型清單，這些字串做為工作階段狀態值的金鑰。

trans-unit.source: A `null` return value indicates to a session-state provider that the provider should return all session state values.
trans-unit.target: A`null`傳回值，表示工作階段狀態提供者提供者應該傳回所有工作階段狀態的值。
